pull.title: build: add Qt Creator Makefile.am.user to .gitignore
pull.body: Opening Bitcoin with Qt Creator via the Makefile.am generates a Makefile.am.user. Would be handy to have this file ignored. Looking around I can see this file has snuck into a few downstream projects. I do personally find myself editing commits to remove this file when I've not been paying attention. There's got to have been a few PRs with this file accidentally attached.

[build] .gitignore add Qt Creator Makefile.am.user

Opening Bitcoin with Qt Creator via the Makefile.am generates a Makefile.am.user. Would be handy to have this file ignored. Looking around I can see this file has snuck into a few downstream projects. I do personally find myself editing commits to remove this file when I've not been paying attention. There's got to have been a few PRs with this file accidentally attached.
